\newlabel{fig:tuned_lens_sweep}{{9}{15}{Layer vs.\ KL(HMM $\|$ HMM-target tuned lens) vs.\ $R^2$ for all 6 HMM configurations. Black line (left axis): belief-state probe $R^2$. Colored dashed line (right axis): KL divergence. Both Mess3 and Fern achieve near-zero KL at the early layers where $R^2$ peaks}{figure.9}{}}
