\newlabel{fig:pairwise_r2_matrix}{{15}{20}{$4 \times 4$ cross-regression matrix. Each entry shows the $R^2$ of a linear probe trained to predict the column's theoretical target from the row's activations. Diagonal entries (boxed) are highest in each row, confirming that each stage preferentially encodes its matched target}{figure.15}{}}
